NAME
    Spork - Slide Presentations (Only Really Kwiki)

SYNOPSIS
        mkdir my-slideshow
        cd my-slideshow
        spork -new
        vim config.yaml
        vim Spork.slides
        spork -make
        spork -start

DESCRIPTION
    Spork lets you create HTML slideshow presentations easily. It comes with
    a sample slideshow. All you need is a text editor, a browser and a
    topic.

    Follow the steps above, and Fanny's your aunt.

SEE ALSO
    Kwiki, Spoon

